  "text": "The DNA was extracted from tumor-frozen specimen and paraffin-embedded tissues using QIAamp DNA Tissue kits (Qiagen, Valencia, CA, USA) according to the manufacturer's instructions. Exons 18-21 of the EGFR gene were amplified using polymerase chain reaction (PCR) and then DNA sequencing reaction and subjected to electrophoresis using the ABI PRISM 3130XL System (Applied Biosystems, Foster City, CA, USA) as previously described [CITATION_1] .",
